favourite.article: YES! We will claim this divine power!!! Not be ashamed of our WONDERFUL CHRIST! Praise the Lord for this wonderful hymn to show us more of our WONDERFUL CHRIST!
Yes I will claim this divine power.

O bountiful supply of the Spirit, we give ourselves to YOU, a people of all ages, experiencing YOUR living, fully enjoying YOU! our Awesome God! Praying for all YOUR comings & goings &all borders! Go freely unto the coming! we say enemies be blind, dumb and deaf, Thank YOU LORD for Overshadowing everything pertaining to YOURSELF &for YOUR return! we love YOU our beloved God:):) YOU Are, I AM. Praise the LORD:):)
